prodNameC: 羅氏免疫分析愛滋病毒品管液
ingredientsDesc:
Reagents - working solutions
• PC HIV1: 2 bottles, each for 2 mL of control serum
   Human serum, negative for HIV (antigen and antibodies); preservative.
   Target value range for the cutoff index:
   HIV combi: 0.00-0.67
   HIV Ag: ≤ 0.80
• PC HIV2: 2 bottles, each for 2 mL of control serum
   Human serum, positive for anti-HIV antibodies; preservative.
   Target value range for the cutoff index:
   HIV combi: 5.5-19.8
   HIV Ag: No target value. Do not use PC HIV2 for the Elecsys HIV Ag assay.
• PC HIV3: 2 bottles, each for 2 mL of control serum
   HIV p24-Ag (E. coli, rDNA) approx. 400 pg/mL in citrate
   buffer, pH 4.0; preservative.
   Target value range for the cutoff index:
   HIV combi: 7.0-22.1
   HIV Ag: 95-250
applicantName: 台灣羅氏醫療診斷設備股份有限公司
applicantAddr: 台北市中山區民權東路3段2號10樓
efficacy: Elecsys PreciControl HIV是使用在Elecsys和cobas e免疫分析儀上，以供Elecsys HIV combi免疫分析法的品質管控之用。
